title: Star Fems (Restored)
description:
Issues 1-2 of 'Star Fems'

Paragon Publications, 1980 and 1982, 34 and 52 pages

Written by Bill Black,Paul McCusker, Ed Lane, Billy Fugate

Illustrated by John Beatty, Dennis Fujitake, Jerry Ordway, Steve Vance, Marc Hempel, Mike Vosberg, Paul McCusker, Bill Black, Pat Broderick, Mark Heike, Roy Richardson, Stephen Schwartz

This series featured fighting sci-fi babe stories with characters such as Stormy Tempest, Mysta of the Moon, Futura and Syren, amongst others. Kind of kitschy, kind of pulpy, but contrary to the cover image featured above, not actually an "adult" book. But folks have requested more stuff like this and I said I'd post it as I found it, so here ya go.
